title: Venkatesh sings two films
text: After the success of Gopala Gopala, Venkatesh has not announced any new project until now. But as per the latest update, Venky has given a nod to two new projects which will be produced by Suresh Babu. One of them will be directed by Kranthi Madhav of Malli Malli Idhi Rani Roju fame and Maruthi, who is riding high on the success of Bhale Bhale Magadivoy, will wield the other film. Both these projects will be formally launched on Dussera and Venkatesh is making plans to shoot these two projects simultaneously.
